places.name: Estancia El Terruño
places.perex: If agro tourism is your thing, stop by at this farm. Horsbeack riding is only one of the activities you can try here.

places.name: Irurtia Winery

places.name: Canario Luna Amphitheatre

places.name: Cuartel de Dragones

places.name: Playa La Colorada
places.perex: A small beach with white sand has shallow clear water and powdery sand. Go there and enjoy the bathing and the sun!

places.name: Las Delicias Beach
places.perex: It's an usual sunny day in Punta del Este and what could be better than exposing to sun like a butterfly on this beach.

places.name: Feria Artesanal

places.name: Company Bar

places.name: El Pilar Building

places.name: Arroyo Maldonado

places.name: 1949 Hostel Bar

places.name: Sugar Loaf Ocean Club & Spa
